data.description: Welcome home to this gorgeous, countryside retreat! This beauty offers breathtaking views overlooking the Appalachian Mountains! Located just 5 minutes from the angelic Back of the Dragon (a 32 mile drive with captivating scenery and over 300 curves). Less than a 10 minute drive to popular attractions such a Lincolnshire Park which includes a lake, Aqua Park, Kidztown Playground, Splash Pad, walking trails, multiple sports complexes and more! Convenient to town, offering over 6 acres of magnificent mountain views, a 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom beautiful home, 2 garages (parking for up to 6 vehicles), several outbuildings and so much more! Perfect for a mini farm as much of the property already has fencing encompassing! This quaint, move in ready, charming, humble abode is one that you certainly do not want to miss! Contact your favorite agent today to schedule your private tour of this one of a kind charmer!!!
